code: public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {     List<String> params = new ArrayList<>().     params.add(exchange.getIn().getBody(String.class)).     exchange.getOut().setBody(params).     String operation = (String) exchange.getIn().getHeader(CxfConstants.OPERATION_NAME).     LOG.info("The operation name is " + operation).     exchange.getOut().setHeader(CxfConstants.OPERATION_NAME, operation). }
